1
00:00:14,986 --> 00:00:16,096
Nanay...

2
00:00:17,342 --> 00:00:18,832
Kumusta si Gng. Weiling?

3
00:00:25,122 --> 00:00:27,332
Mayroon akong cardiomyopathy,

4
00:00:28,622 --> 00:00:29,682
malamang dahil sa lahat ng inuman

5
00:00:30,432 --> 00:00:32,022
pagkatapos ng nangyari noon.

6
00:00:33,212 --> 00:00:34,582
Pero hindi ko pa nasasabi kay Lalin.

7
00:00:35,332 --> 00:00:36,532
Ayokong mag-alala siya.

8
00:00:38,342 --> 00:00:39,932
Kaya siya nauuwi sa ganito dahil sa akin.

9
00:00:43,102 --> 00:00:44,102
Huwag mong sisihin ang sarili mo.

10
00:00:44,842 --> 00:00:46,202
Nandito ka sa tabi ko ngayon.

11
00:00:50,842 --> 00:00:52,812
Hindi ba kasama mo si Lalin?

12
00:00:55,642 --> 00:00:57,252
Magtatanong sana ako

13
00:00:59,502 --> 00:01:00,502
kung nasaan siya.

14
00:01:01,392 --> 00:01:03,052
Nauna na siyang umalis sa akin, 'di ba?

15
00:01:11,412 --> 00:01:12,142
Matalino...

16
00:01:15,142 --> 00:01:16,222
Buwan!

17
00:01:16,752 --> 00:01:18,572
Nasaan ka? Sino ang gumawa nito sa iyo?

18
00:01:19,262 --> 00:01:20,202
Kasama! Lalin!

19
00:01:20,522 --> 00:01:21,492
Ano ito?

20
00:01:21,682 --> 00:01:22,932
Bakit mo binihag ang anak ko?

21
00:01:23,272 --> 00:01:24,612
Bb. Weiling, wala itong kinalaman sa iyo.

22
00:01:25,142 --> 00:01:27,262
Si Arisa ang nagpasimula ng lahat ng ito.

23
00:01:27,522 --> 00:01:29,272
Kung hindi niya sana ginulo ang asawa ko,

24
00:01:29,442 --> 00:01:31,202
Hindi na sana kailangan nandito si Ms. Lalin ngayon.

25
00:01:31,542 --> 00:01:32,412
Arisa,

26
00:01:32,732 --> 00:01:33,732
Saan mo ba dinala si Pin?

27
00:01:33,782 --> 00:01:34,892
Huminahon ka.

28
00:01:35,422 --> 00:01:36,422
Makinig ka sa akin.

29
00:01:36,682 --> 00:01:38,082
Hayaan mo na lang si Pin.

30
00:01:38,622 --> 00:01:39,682
Pakiusap, magtiwala ka sa akin.

31
00:01:39,762 --> 00:01:40,342
Matalino,

32
00:01:41,432 --> 00:01:42,532
pag-usapan natin.

33
00:01:43,432 --> 00:01:44,492
Ano ang gusto mo?

34
00:01:44,602 --> 00:01:46,412
Ibalik mo na lang sa akin ang asawa ko,

35
00:01:46,602 --> 00:01:47,882
at matatapos din ang lahat!

36
00:01:48,582 --> 00:01:51,442
Kung hindi mo dadalhin si Pin sa akin mamayang gabi,

37
00:01:54,082 --> 00:01:55,342
walang dahilan

38
00:01:55,862 --> 00:01:56,982
para hayaan kong mabuhay si Ms. Lalin.

39
00:01:57,122 --> 00:01:59,492
Wit, kumalma ka.

40
00:01:59,732 --> 00:02:00,612
Nagmamakaawa ako sa iyo.

41
00:02:00,882 --> 00:02:02,732
Gawin mo lang ang hinihiling ko,

42
00:02:03,492 --> 00:02:05,092
at huwag kang magdala ng kahit sinong pulis;

43
00:02:05,422 --> 00:02:07,812
kung hindi, para na ring patay si Ms. Lalin!

44
00:02:08,062 --> 00:02:08,602
Matalino!

45
00:02:08,642 --> 00:02:09,932
Matalino, huwag! Matalino!

46
00:02:09,972 --> 00:02:10,892
Madali!

47
00:02:10,922 --> 00:02:11,742
Bitawan mo ako!

48
00:02:11,772 --> 00:02:12,622
Saan ka pupunta?!

49
00:02:12,652 --> 00:02:14,612
- Tutulungan ko ang anak ko! - Hindi mo kaya!

50
00:02:14,652 --> 00:02:15,572
Hindi ka pa rin maayos.

51
00:02:15,602 --> 00:02:17,462
Paano ka makakaalis ngayon? Paano kung sumiklab ito?!

52
00:02:17,822 --> 00:02:18,612
Ms. Weiling!

53
00:02:20,022 --> 00:02:21,512
Lahat ng ito

54
00:02:21,932 --> 00:02:23,242
nangyari dahil sa akin,

55
00:02:24,042 --> 00:02:26,012
dahil sa kung gaano ako kadesperado noon.

56
00:02:26,952 --> 00:02:28,372
Kung hindi ko sana siya ginalit

57
00:02:28,942 --> 00:02:30,632
dahil gusto kitang talunin,

58
00:02:31,022 --> 00:02:33,302
Hindi sana hahantong sa ganito si Lalin.

59
00:02:34,412 --> 00:02:36,182
Nagsimula ito sa akin,

60
00:02:36,332 --> 00:02:37,942
kaya dapat sa akin na lang ito matapos.

61
00:02:43,512 --> 00:02:44,942
Hindi ba't masyadong mapanganib ito?

62
00:02:45,252 --> 00:02:46,922
Hindi ba dapat hayaan na lang natin ang mga pulis na humawak nito?

63
00:02:47,912 --> 00:02:50,762
Hindi ko hahayaang may mang-agaw ng kamay sa taong mahal ko.

64
00:02:50,862 --> 00:02:52,362
Huwag kang mag-alala, Nay.

65
00:02:55,862 --> 00:02:57,792
Kailangan mong maging maingat talaga, mahal.

66
00:02:58,932 --> 00:03:01,122
Hindi ko rin kayang mawala ka.

67
00:03:02,722 --> 00:03:03,592
Sige.

68
00:03:07,812 --> 00:03:08,882
Iiwan ko na ito sa iyo.

69
00:03:17,872 --> 00:03:18,532
Hoy,

70
00:03:18,932 --> 00:03:20,072
Papunta na ako para tulungan si Lalin.

71
00:03:20,352 --> 00:03:21,452
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin?

72
00:03:21,622 --> 00:03:22,622
Anong nangyari, Boss?

73
00:03:22,662 --> 00:03:24,522
Binihag siya ni Wit.

74
00:03:24,562 --> 00:03:26,002
Pupunta ka ba roon nang mag-isa?

75
00:03:26,042 --> 00:03:27,582
Sana sumama ako sa iyo, Boss.

76
00:04:22,302 --> 00:04:24,072
Pakawalan mo na ako.

77
00:04:24,342 --> 00:04:25,202
Hoy!

78
00:04:25,602 --> 00:04:27,782
Pakawalan mo na ako, Wit.

79
00:04:28,602 --> 00:04:29,602
Matalino...

80
00:04:30,312 --> 00:04:32,642
Pwede ba nating pag-usapan na lang ang mga bagay-bagay?

81
00:04:32,682 --> 00:04:33,772
Matalino!

82
00:04:38,352 --> 00:04:40,542
Wit, pakitanggal mo nga 'to sa akin.

83
00:04:40,582 --> 00:04:42,402
Huwag mo naman sanang gawin ito.

84
00:04:48,262 --> 00:04:49,262
Matalino,

85
00:04:51,012 --> 00:04:54,492
wala itong maitutulong.

86
00:04:56,392 --> 00:04:57,762
Kahit na ganito,

87
00:04:58,062 --> 00:05:00,302
Hindi na babalik sa iyo si Ms. Pin.

88
00:05:04,122 --> 00:05:04,812
Ginang Buwan,

89
00:05:07,532 --> 00:05:08,502
hindi mo maiintindihan.

90
00:05:10,122 --> 00:05:11,922
Mahigit sampung taon na kaming magkasama ni Pin.

91
00:05:13,412 --> 00:05:14,412
Lahat ng aking nagawa,

92
00:05:15,252 --> 00:05:16,942
lahat ng trabahong ginawa ko ay para sa kanya!

93
00:05:19,972 --> 00:05:22,242
Kahit ano pa man, mahal niya ako, at babalik siya!

94
00:05:22,342 --> 00:05:24,932
Hindi 'yan pag-ibig, Wit.

95
00:05:27,052 --> 00:05:28,482
Hawakan mo lang siya

96
00:05:28,512 --> 00:05:31,252
para masiguro mo sa sarili mo na may kasama ka pa rin sa buhay mo.

97
00:05:32,432 --> 00:05:33,092
Matalino,

98
00:05:33,422 --> 00:05:34,322
Maniwala ka sa akin.

99
00:05:34,362 --> 00:05:35,282
Huwag mong gawin ito.

100
00:05:35,542 --> 00:05:37,122
Wala nang mas makakabuti pa nito.

101
00:05:37,502 --> 00:05:38,542
Pakawalan mo na ako.

102
00:05:38,572 --> 00:05:39,312
- Hindi. - Huwag...

103
00:05:39,352 --> 00:05:40,432
Huwag mo naman sanang gawin ito.

104
00:05:40,462 --> 00:05:41,412
Hindi mo maiintindihan!

105
00:05:43,342 --> 00:05:44,812
Ang ginawa ko

106
00:05:46,912 --> 00:05:47,992
ay wala na sa pag-ibig.

107
00:05:49,652 --> 00:05:51,342
At lahat ng ito ay nagiba

108
00:05:51,552 --> 00:05:52,812
dahil kay Arisa!

109
00:06:09,052 --> 00:06:10,412
Huwag mong gawin ito...

110
00:06:11,622 --> 00:06:12,892
Pakawalan mo na ako...

111
00:06:56,592 --> 00:06:57,322
I-pin...

112
00:07:21,122 --> 00:07:21,812
I-pin...

113
00:07:33,462 --> 00:07:34,932
Arisa!

114
00:07:37,282 --> 00:07:37,852
Naku!

115
00:07:39,432 --> 00:07:41,252
Tulong po!

116
00:07:41,462 --> 00:07:42,222
Tulong...

117
00:07:43,652 --> 00:07:44,412
Ayyy, alis na!

118
00:07:44,762 --> 00:07:45,432
Hoy!

119
00:07:47,392 --> 00:07:49,562
Tulungan mo ako! Pakiusap!

120
00:07:55,612 --> 00:07:56,252
Ginang Moon...

121
00:07:56,292 --> 00:07:57,622
- Bb. Aiy... - Ayos ka lang ba?

122
00:07:57,652 --> 00:07:58,612
Ayos ka lang ba?

123
00:07:58,942 --> 00:07:59,942
Sandali lang.

124
00:08:10,872 --> 00:08:12,422
Sige, sige...

125
00:08:13,902 --> 00:08:14,902
Sandali lang.

126
00:08:19,152 --> 00:08:20,172
Tara na.

127
00:08:46,912 --> 00:08:47,612
Aray...

128
00:09:06,742 --> 00:09:08,082
Ibalik mo sa akin si Pin.

129
00:09:08,112 --> 00:09:10,962
Hinding-hindi makakasama ni Pin ang isang halimaw na katulad mo!

130
00:09:11,512 --> 00:09:13,022
Paano mo nagawa 'to kay Lalin?

131
00:09:13,152 --> 00:09:14,152
Paano mo nagawa?!

132
00:09:14,352 --> 00:09:15,152
Hindi!!

133
00:09:15,202 --> 00:09:17,052
Ibalik mo sa akin ang Pin ko!

134
00:10:05,132 --> 00:10:07,182
Dito binihag si Ms. Lalin.

135
00:10:07,382 --> 00:10:09,072
Sige, kakalat tayo at maghahanap.

136
00:10:09,282 --> 00:10:11,502
Dalawa sa kaliwa, dalawa sa likuran, at dalawa sa harap. Sige!

137
00:10:25,222 --> 00:10:25,722
Sa ganitong paraan.

138
00:10:26,762 --> 00:10:27,332
Tara na.

139
00:11:01,002 --> 00:11:01,832
Opisyal,

140
00:11:01,942 --> 00:11:03,172
doon dumaan ang lalaki.

141
00:11:03,942 --> 00:11:04,782
Kopyahin!

142
00:11:05,202 --> 00:11:06,202
Ayos ka lang ba?

143
00:11:07,032 --> 00:11:08,092
Huminga nang dahan-dahan.

144
00:11:08,302 --> 00:11:09,882
Ligtas ka na ngayon.

145
00:11:12,182 --> 00:11:13,122
Dahan-dahan lang.

146
00:11:14,052 --> 00:11:15,232
Huminga nang dahan-dahan.

147
00:11:16,362 --> 00:11:17,622
Ayos ka na ngayon.

148
00:11:23,822 --> 00:11:25,302
- Naku... - Uy, nakakatagal ka ba?

149
00:11:25,822 --> 00:11:27,522
Dahan-dahan lang. Dahan-dahan lang.

150
00:11:28,152 --> 00:11:29,152
Kaya mo namang ituloy, 'di ba?

151
00:11:29,662 --> 00:11:30,512
Sige.

152
00:11:32,922 --> 00:11:33,622
Halika rito!

153
00:11:33,652 --> 00:11:34,412
Hoy!

154
00:11:35,502 --> 00:11:36,082
Bitawan mo ako!

155
00:11:36,432 --> 00:11:37,342
- Bitawan mo ako! - Tumigil ka!

156
00:11:37,382 --> 00:11:38,672
- Talino! - Tumigil!

157
00:11:40,512 --> 00:11:42,032
Walang kinalaman si Lalin dito.

158
00:11:43,152 --> 00:11:45,092
Wala siyang kinalaman dito.

159
00:11:45,232 --> 00:11:46,192
Hayaan mo na siya.

160
00:11:46,222 --> 00:11:47,182
Sumuko ako.

161
00:11:48,142 --> 00:11:49,752
Sa lahat ng bagay.

162
00:11:49,912 --> 00:11:51,232
Huwag mo akong sabihan kung ano ang gagawin.

163
00:11:52,702 --> 00:11:54,412
Kinuha mo si Pin sa akin.

164
00:11:55,492 --> 00:11:56,862
Kukunin ko rin si Lalin sa iyo!

165
00:11:56,892 --> 00:11:58,782
Huwag! Huwag! Huwag! Huwag! Huwag....

166
00:11:59,172 --> 00:12:00,022
Huwag!

167
00:12:01,492 --> 00:12:02,562
Huminahon ka.

168
00:12:03,122 --> 00:12:04,122
Kumalma ka lang.

169
00:12:05,002 --> 00:12:06,682
Pwede natin itong pag-usapan, Wit.

170
00:12:08,092 --> 00:12:09,002
Sumusuko na talaga ako.

171
00:12:09,032 --> 00:12:10,072
Hindi na ako nakikinig sa mga kalokohan mo!

172
00:12:11,162 --> 00:12:12,332
Kahit ano pa man,

173
00:12:12,522 --> 00:12:14,552
Pareho kayong mamamatay ngayon!

174
00:12:14,592 --> 00:12:15,662
Tumigil! Tumigil! Tumigil...

175
00:12:15,702 --> 00:12:16,362
- Tama na... - Tumigil na!

176
00:12:19,512 --> 00:12:20,452
Ibaba mo na ang baril, ngayon na!

177
00:12:22,102 --> 00:12:22,902
Sabi ko, ibaba mo ang baril!

178
00:12:33,812 --> 00:12:34,812
Arisa...

179
00:12:37,352 --> 00:12:38,662
Niloko mo ako!

180
00:12:52,432 --> 00:12:53,432
Tiyo Mek!

181
00:12:56,952 --> 00:12:57,952
Argh! / ...

182
00:13:02,602 --> 00:13:03,532
Tiyo!

183
00:13:03,972 --> 00:13:06,292
Sinabi ko na sa'yo na ayoko nang makita ang mukha mo!

184
00:13:06,472 --> 00:13:08,372
Bakit ka pumunta rito?!

185
00:13:11,142 --> 00:13:12,012
Bakit mo ginawa...

186
00:13:17,712 --> 00:13:21,522
Nangako ako sa tatay mo...

187
00:13:23,632 --> 00:13:26,522
na aalagaan kita nang mabuti.

188
00:13:31,402 --> 00:13:32,482
Ako...

189
00:13:35,492 --> 00:13:37,652
Natupad ko na rin sa wakas ang pangako ko.

190
00:13:46,262 --> 00:13:47,322
Tiyo Mek...

191
00:13:47,492 --> 00:13:48,412
Tiyo Mek!

192
00:13:48,632 --> 00:13:49,932
Tiyo Mek!

193
00:13:56,522 --> 00:13:57,682
Tiyo Mek...

194
00:14:13,642 --> 00:14:16,242
Taimtim kitang pinapatawad sa lahat ng iyong nagawa,

195
00:14:17,132 --> 00:14:20,812
at salamat sa pag-aalaga mo kay Kee para sa akin.

196
00:14:28,512 --> 00:14:30,452
Salamat, Tiyo,

197
00:14:34,832 --> 00:14:38,392
sa pagprotekta sa akin sa buong buhay ko,

198
00:14:42,222 --> 00:14:44,542
kahit hanggang sa huling hininga mo.

199
00:15:06,662 --> 00:15:08,832
Tapos na ang lahat, sinta.

200
00:15:14,102 --> 00:15:16,412
Kung gusto mong umiyak,

201
00:15:17,422 --> 00:15:18,902
ilabas mo lahat,

202
00:15:22,442 --> 00:15:24,142
at mula ngayon,

203
00:15:25,532 --> 00:15:27,972
magagandang bagay lang ang darating sa atin.

204
00:15:58,512 --> 00:16:00,132
Kahit na pasado na siya,

205
00:16:00,272 --> 00:16:02,322
siya pa rin ang may kasalanan.

206
00:16:05,272 --> 00:16:07,462
Huwag mong mabuhay sa paghihiganti.

207
00:16:08,002 --> 00:16:10,252
Sapat na ang mga taong nakita kong nagdurusa dahil dito.

208
00:16:11,802 --> 00:16:14,602
Pinakamabuti... ang mabuhay sa kasalukuyan.

209
00:16:17,142 --> 00:16:18,832
Wala akong ibig sabihin doon.

210
00:16:19,632 --> 00:16:21,062
Gumaan lang ang loob ko

211
00:16:21,332 --> 00:16:22,882
para malaman kung sino ang nasa likod ng nangyari sa tatay ko.

212
00:16:25,882 --> 00:16:27,732
Napatawad ko na siya ngayon.

213
00:16:29,622 --> 00:16:30,622
Mabuti iyan.

214
00:16:31,062 --> 00:16:34,602
Gayunpaman, nakikiramay ako sa nangyari sa tatay mo.

215
00:16:35,602 --> 00:16:37,052
Ang galing mo pala talaga.

216
00:16:37,382 --> 00:16:40,732
Siguradong proud na proud sa'yo ang tatay mo kahit saan.

217
00:16:42,802 --> 00:16:43,902
Salamat.

218
00:16:45,302 --> 00:16:46,922
At least, may maganda namang mangyayari

219
00:16:47,512 --> 00:16:49,372
lumalabas mula rito.

220
00:16:51,502 --> 00:16:52,502
Aling bahagi?

221
00:16:55,392 --> 00:16:57,202
Ang bahagi kung saan nakilala kita.

222
00:17:05,622 --> 00:17:06,622
Tama,

223
00:17:07,482 --> 00:17:09,692
kahit anong ibigay mo, matapang ka pa rin.

224
00:17:11,242 --> 00:17:14,422
Alam mo naman kung gaano kalaking panganib ang nilalagay mo sa sarili mo, 'di ba?

225
00:17:16,162 --> 00:17:17,152
Oo,

226
00:17:17,972 --> 00:17:19,782
Alam kong mapanganib iyon.

227
00:17:19,812 --> 00:17:23,032
Sa totoo lang, ayaw akong payagan ng boss ko,

228
00:17:25,022 --> 00:17:27,642
pero hindi ko talaga siya pwedeng hayaang mag-isa doon.

229
00:17:30,412 --> 00:17:33,002
Kung gayon, maaari ba akong magtanong sa iyo?

230
00:17:34,422 --> 00:17:37,952
Noong araw na iyon, nandoon ka lang ba talaga para magbalita?

231
00:17:42,942 --> 00:17:44,572
Hindi ako naroon para sa coverage.

232
00:17:45,642 --> 00:17:46,982
Pumunta ako roon para tulungan ka.

233
00:17:52,742 --> 00:17:53,742
Salamat.

234
00:17:57,822 --> 00:17:58,672
Tara na.

235
00:18:24,948 --> 00:18:26,818
Naging maayos ang lahat.

236
00:18:27,378 --> 00:18:29,328
Malamang ay maaari na siyang ma-discharge ngayong gabi.

237
00:18:29,818 --> 00:18:33,638
Ang natitira na lang ay siguraduhing iniinom ng pasyente ang lahat ng kanyang mga gamot.

238
00:18:34,298 --> 00:18:35,878
At higit na mahalaga,

239
00:18:35,958 --> 00:18:37,438
dapat niyang iwasan nang lubusan ang pag-inom

240
00:18:37,898 --> 00:18:42,918
at dapat ninyo siyang bigyan ng babala na huwag masyadong magsikap;

241
00:18:43,648 --> 00:18:46,408
o kung hindi ay maaaring magkaroon ng pagbabalik sa dati.

242
00:18:48,318 --> 00:18:49,858
Maraming salamat po, Doktor.

243
00:18:49,958 --> 00:18:50,958
Pasensya na.

244
00:18:59,308 --> 00:19:00,308
Nanay,

245
00:19:00,768 --> 00:19:03,678
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin na ganito ka pala kalala ang sakit mo?

246
00:19:05,008 --> 00:19:07,308
Simula nang hilingin kong umuwi ka na,

247
00:19:08,378 --> 00:19:10,198
Palagi akong handa.

248
00:19:12,418 --> 00:19:13,418
Hindi mo talaga alam...

249
